# Gmail Credentials Configuration
# Lines starting with # are comments and will be ignored
#
# INSTRUCTIONS:
# 1. Copy this file: cp config_credentials.txt.example config_credentials.txt
# 2. Edit config_credentials.txt and add your Gmail credentials
# 3. Get Gmail App Password from: https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
